{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act26side_level_act26side_05_end","storyGroup":"act26side","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act26side_level_act26side_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HE-5","storyName":"主在圣殿中","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"人会因饥饿而堕为异样的怪物，怪物却也会因舐犊之情，重新变回一位母亲。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act26side/level_act26side_05_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act26side_05","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["修道院主教","？？？","杰拉尔德","费德里科","扭曲的怪物","艾伦戴尔","艾丝塔拉","“扭曲的怪物”","里凯莱","克莱芒","莱蒙德","赫曼"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在拉特兰时，我是很少祷告的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":9},{"type":"subtitle","text":"当然，这并不是说那个时期我的信仰有瑕，或是说相较现在我更自大懒惰，我也没法证明现在的我更加笃信，更谦逊勤勉。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":10},{"type":"subtitle","text":"只不过是尚在拉特兰时，受到当时环境的影响，我认为许多事是没有必要的。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"在拉特兰，所有为人所追寻的东西就在那里，圣城的赐福就在那里。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"720","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"无处不在，无处不有。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","text":"萨科塔清楚这一点。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","id":15},{"type":"dialog","id":16},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":17},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":18},{"type":"charslot","id":19},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"“主啊，请您原谅......”","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"“我曾发过誓言，要善待所有求助者，无论是谁，需一视同仁，尽我所能地提供帮助。”","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"“但我食言了。”","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"“我已无法回应渴求救助之人，我无法让他们留下，只因我们的物资不足，无法负担。”","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"“在一群人与另一群人之间，我必须做出选择......”","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"“......选择。是的，我早已做过不止一次选择......”","id":29},{"type":"text","text":"“可选择是错误的。而今，我已无法忍受更多错误。”","id":30},{"type":"text","text":"“我已不能再背弃我的信仰，为救人而舍弃，为多数而抛下少数！”","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"“拉特兰......我久未重逢的故乡......”","id":32},{"type":"text","text":"“为何仅有拉特兰才是乐园？”","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"“若通向我所信的前提，乃是背弃我脑中高悬的指引；若只有借助异教，才可真正消除障碍......”","id":34},{"type":"text","text":"“......再过不久，一切都将得出答案。”","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"“倘若我们的主真的存在，就请您宽恕我的罪过......”","id":36},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialog","id":38},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.7","id":39},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":40},{"type":"text","text":"“——！”","id":41},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"image","id":45},{"type":"charslot","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":47},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_bg_39_g12_anbandonspace.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":50},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":51},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":52},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"什么人！","id":54,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":55},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.6","channel":"step1","loop":"false","id":56},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"step1","fadetime":"1.5","id":57},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"150,0","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","id":58},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"......","id":60,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walkfast","volume":"0.4","channel":"step2","loop":"false","id":62},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"step2","fadetime":"1","id":63},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","posfrom":"150,0","posto":"-150,0","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"1","id":64},{"type":"delay","time":"1.1","id":65},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovementsp","volume":"1","id":66},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.8","xstrength":"12","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","posfrom":"-150,0","posto":"60,0","afrom":"1","ato":"1","duration":"0.6","id":68},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":69},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","posfrom":"-60,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"0.5","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":72},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.7","focus":"l","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎，别动手，别动手，有话好好说。","id":74,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我找了您好一会呢，主教阁下。","id":75,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":78},{"type":"charslot","id":79},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":81},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":82,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":84},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":85},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":86},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"最近食物缺得厉害，只有这点东西能招待客人，你不介意吧？","id":89,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"介意也没别的了，味道可能不太好，不过只求填饱肚子的话勉强还可以。","id":90,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"暂时没有进食的必要。","id":92,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"吃吧。都拿出来了，别浪费。","id":94,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":96,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"萨卡兹领袖杰拉尔德，你认识那两名黎博利孩童。","id":98,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......你总是这么直接吗？","id":100,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"别喊我领袖，我见过真正的萨卡兹的王，我一介猎户配不上这称呼。","id":101,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"为什么自称猎户？","id":103,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"因为我确实是个猎户。我靠打猎养活自己和其他人。","id":105,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"虽然是今天刚到，但我猜你应该已经了解这里的情况了吧。","id":106,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不完全。","id":108,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你带着萨卡兹在这里生活，你们是后来者，但曾经融入得很好。","id":109,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"是啊，曾经是不错。","id":111,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"现在你们与其他人产生冲突，根据目前的局势判断，这种冲突很大可能会继续升级。","id":113,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"你的判断没错。所以我们就要走了。","id":115,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"正常情况下，在与其他居民的冲突中，你们会占据上风。","id":117,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这里的原住民中少见擅长战斗的人员，他们缺乏战斗力也是你们被接受的原因之一。","id":118,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"但如今拉特兰的介入让你们失去了在武力上的优势。离开是稳妥的选择。","id":119,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"你很擅长得出合理的解释，执行者阁下。","id":121,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"但从很久之前我就明白，到现在也仍在时刻被提醒——","id":122,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我们的生活从不合理。","id":124,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":125},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#4$1","focus":"none","id":126},{"type":"text","text":"烛光跳动。","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"年长的萨卡兹的视线落在墙壁上，那里映出模糊的虚影，一切差异在此时都不再清晰。","id":128},{"type":"dialog","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我们不会因无法生存而选择离开。","id":131,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"在来到这里之前，老实说，我从未想过能够有这样的生活。","id":132,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"有种种风险，有许多摩擦，但我们被认可、被接纳，我们亲手搭建住所，靠劳动获得粮食......","id":133,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"或许这在你看来很寻常，但对我们来说，这是曾经不敢想象的日子。","id":134,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你们选择离开的真正理由是？","id":136,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"很简单。","id":138,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"就如你所说，我们都能预见将会有的冲突，隔阂已经存在，无人能够修补，我只能眼睁睁地看着一切越来越糟......","id":139,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"现在还只是争吵，只是责怪。可接下来呢？","id":140,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......争吵升级为暴力冲突，普通居民与萨卡兹互相怨恨的可能性很大。","id":142,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",5]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"今晚的火灾或许是一个警示。","id":144,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"现在离开，我们仍是值得怀念的伙伴，是令人惋惜的朋友。","id":145,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"而要是放任那些不舍情绪，再不做出决定......","id":146,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我们将会重新成为世人眼中的萨卡兹——只会挑起争端，在哪里都不受欢迎，没有归处亦没有去处的一群流浪之人。","id":148,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这只是偏见。","id":150,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"对我们来说却是事实。","id":152,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"萨科塔有你们的拉特兰城。","id":153,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"而萨卡兹......我们何曾真正属于过什么地方？","id":154,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":156,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",4]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"所以我想是时候了。","id":158,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"生得晚的那些年轻人可能会不太习惯晚上没有屋檐的生活，不过他们会适应的。","id":159,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"至于今天的那两个孩子......","id":160,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你认识他们。","id":162,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......我确实知道点他们的来历。","id":164,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"修道院内的居民与莱蒙德并不知情。","id":166,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"知道他们存在的人很少。","id":168,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我也只是猜测，他们应该是外来的流浪者，或许是家人遭难，或许是被抛弃，都有可能。","id":169,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"从前斯特凡诺不是没有接纳过类似的流浪者，只是以现在的状况来看，这里很难再负担更多人。","id":170,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"但......有人偷偷收养了这两个孩子。","id":172,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",5]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"你知道是谁。","id":174,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"很少有什么事真的能一直完美地隐瞒下去，特别是在现在这种每一粒稻谷都要被计较的时候。","id":176,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"赫曼收养了他们。每天从自己那份口粮里省一部分，还有几回偷偷动了狩猎的猎物，我发觉之后都替她补上了。","id":177,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"就算这样，他们的日子仍然过得比较艰难。","id":178,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这位赫曼女士现在在哪？","id":180,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......我也正在想她去哪了。今天她本该带着狩猎的猎物回来，但到现在也没有消息。","id":182,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我们还没找到她。她失踪了。","id":183,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"不论如何，我由衷地希望她不会做什么傻事。","id":184,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"失踪？不，不对。","id":186,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"你的意思是？","id":188,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",8]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"赫曼女士秘密收养两个孩童，平时不会允许他们独自外出，艾伦戴尔和艾丝塔拉出现在圣堂不是意外。","id":190,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",5]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......有人带着他们出门。","id":192,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",2]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"赫曼女士的家在哪？我需要亲自去查看。","id":194,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":195},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":196},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":197},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"charslot","id":199},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":201},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":202},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":203},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_calm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":204,"musicid":2},{"type":"text","text":"破旧的木屋对幼小的孩子们来说是一处港湾。","id":205},{"type":"text","text":"因成年人无力养育而像是不被需要的废弃品一般遭到抛弃，又在流浪于荒野、奄奄一息时，被毫无关系的萨卡兹拾起。","id":206},{"type":"text","text":"被偷偷领到这间破破烂烂的小屋，这里有漏风的木板和不保暖的被褥，有破旧但整洁的衣裳，还有不美味但足以果腹的食物。","id":207},{"type":"text","text":"尽管它无法完全抵御寒风，就算将家中所有能够御寒的布料堆在一起，再把冬衣紧紧裹在身上，蚀骨的寒意仍让人在睡梦中也不禁蜷缩。","id":208},{"type":"text","text":"但这是“家”。家里还有妈妈。","id":209},{"type":"text","text":"这里就是孩子们最能够安心的地方。","id":210},{"type":"dialog","id":211},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":213},{"type":"charslot","id":214},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":216},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":217},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":218},{"type":"text","text":"细小的呼吸声并未被不速之客惊扰。","id":219},{"type":"text","text":"它们依旧平稳、绵长。","id":220},{"type":"text","text":"狰狞扭曲的阴影投洒在孩子们身上。","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扭曲的怪物","text":"（古怪的轻语）","id":222,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扭曲的怪物","text":"......饿、吃......","id":223,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"唔......","id":224,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","volume":"0.7","id":226},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"（翻身）","id":228,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扭曲的怪物","text":"吃、吃......","id":229,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扭曲的怪物","text":"冷......","id":230,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":231},{"type":"text","text":"失去曾经形态的怪物发出低沉古怪的吟语。","id":232},{"type":"text","text":"那片始终停留的影子终于有了动作。","id":233},{"type":"text","text":"在月光下，怪物粗长有力的尾部探向前方，带着潮湿气息的尖端扫过孩子稚嫩的面颊，随即——","id":234},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cardboard","volume":"0.6","id":238},{"type":"charslot","id":239},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":241},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":243},{"type":"text","text":"它落在了柔软无力的，小小的“监牢”里。","id":244},{"type":"text","text":"艾丝塔拉和艾伦戴尔仍在睡梦之中。只是身体下意识地，靠向那股让人感到安心的气息。","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"扭曲的怪物","text":"......冷......","id":246,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾伦戴尔","text":"呼......呼......","id":247,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丝塔拉","text":"妈妈......","id":248,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"啊......饿......吃、吃......冷......","id":249,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"......","id":250,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"盖上......盖上......","id":251,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"冷......盖上......","id":252,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"艾......伦......萨拉......","id":255,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":256},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":257},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":259},{"type":"image","id":260},{"type":"charslot","id":261},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6c/Avg_bg_39_g12_anbandonspace.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":262},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#5$1","id":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","id":264},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":265},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":266,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":268},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"主教阁下做了什么？","id":270,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",4]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我只不过是在此告解，来自拉特兰的执行者，你应该知道此时不能偷听。","id":272,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",5]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"哎，别误会，我当然没有听到阁下告解的内容。","id":274,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"当然啦，阁下应该也知道，我问的不是这个，也不是想知道阁下之前派了什么人去敲钟，怎么安排修道院众人的饮食......","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我问的是从顶层圣堂传来的气味。","id":276,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"你分辨得出那种助燃物的味道？......格芬区的铳械工厂，如今还在吗？","id":278,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"哈哈，据我所知，它们依然为各大学院供给练习用的铳械。","id":280,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"当然，燃烧弹也不例外。","id":281,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"......唯有圣城存续千年。","id":283,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我能感觉到阁下很难过。唉，应该得怪费德里科那小子，办事总是这么直接。","id":285,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"不过目前只是建筑的一角烧毁了而已，一切都还留有余地，大家还是可以安稳地回到拉特兰，阁下觉得呢？","id":286,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"你恐怕找错人了。","id":288,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"拆用修道院内旧军火的方法，我早就教给了所有人。燃料有限，冬天很长。","id":289,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"但你若是认为，我是那场火灾的教唆者......我无意反驳。","id":290,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"别这么说嘛，我们还是找个地方坐下来，再好好聊一聊，怎么样？谈出一个双方都能接受的方案。","id":292,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"——聊一聊？方案？呵。","id":294,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"有哪一种方案不用在人与人之间做选择？我已经陈述过我的信念，你们难道当真能让步？","id":295,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"七年前，这一地区遭遇大旱，一队难民流浪到停泊在荒野中的修道院，请求我们收留，但我对他们关上了大门。","id":296,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"他们跌跌撞撞，几乎是爬进荒野深处。那不是我第一次注视那样的场景。","id":297,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"但我向主起誓，那会是最后一次。","id":298,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"执行者，我的信念难道有错？","id":299,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"不不，您当然是正确的，我理解您的悲痛。","id":301,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我也不得不承认，拉特兰有它力不能及的地方。","id":302,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"或者说，律法有它不完善的地方。","id":303,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"你......","id":305,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"我会思考，自然就会质疑。","id":307,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"只不过......就算有不完美的地方，现在的拉特兰对我来说却也已经足够好了，我不希望有任何人或事，威胁到这种平静与和谐。","id":308,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"主教阁下，我想您应该能够理解这种感觉吧？","id":309,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"......","id":311,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"要是我们现在达成协议，阁下不做节外生枝的事情，那我说服某些同事也会比较容易。","id":313,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"你们谁都不动手，这趟外勤任务就可以完成得轻松一点。","id":314,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"即使不能保证所有人都回到拉特兰，我觉得，也没必要搞得所有人都回不去拉特兰嘛。","id":315,"figure":["avg_npc_372_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"拉特兰的使者，拉特兰之于你，正如此处之于我。","id":317,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我想你我之间已无再谈下去的必要。","id":318,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_923_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"——请回吧，不要再打扰我告解了。","id":320,"figure":["avg_npc_923_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":321},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":323},{"type":"charslot","id":324},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/cb/Avg_bg_39_g1_monasteryentrance.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":326},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":327},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":328},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#10$1","duration":"0.5","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_931_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":330},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":331},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"莱蒙德？这么晚了，怎么还不回去休息？","id":333,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_931_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"......是你啊，克莱芒。","id":335,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"没什么，我还有点事。","id":336,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"今天的事，实在很对不起......","id":338,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",4]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_931_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"别在意了，反正我们也要走了。","id":340,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"......嗯。","id":342,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"你们打算什么时候出发......？","id":343,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",4]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_931_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"看杰拉尔德老大的意思，明早不论如何都会动身。","id":345,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"应该是在明早参加完晨会之后吧。","id":346,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"晨会......","id":348,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",4]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_931_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"对了，克莱芒！你......知不知道福尔图娜和德尔菲娜在哪？","id":350,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",10]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"我本来打算喊她们，呃，没什么，总之我找她们有点事。","id":351,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",10]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":352},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"......等等，莱蒙德，杰拉尔德难道没有把那件事告诉你吗？","id":353,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",2]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_931_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":354},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莱蒙德","text":"什么......？你说什么事？","id":355,"figure":["avg_npc_931_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_924_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":356},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"......","id":357,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱芒","text":"德尔菲娜已经......她已经不在了。","id":358,"figure":["avg_npc_924_1",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":359},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":360},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":361},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"charslot","id":363},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/31/Avg_bg_39_g6_villagestreet.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":364},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":365},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":366},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","volume":"1","id":367},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":368},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"......","id":372,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"再......见......","id":373,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":374},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"假设我的听觉没有出问题——这是否是一句告别？","id":375,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$escape_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_escape_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":376,"musicid":4},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"——！","id":378,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":379},{"type":"charslot","id":380},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":381},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","duration":"1","id":382},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":383},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"拥有一定程度的语言能力，看来之前的判断有误。","id":385,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"你......是......","id":387,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"萨科、塔。","id":388,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"保有思考能力，或者说，初步可判断为现阶段残留一定的逻辑思考与自主决断能力。","id":390,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"躯体异化，但可以交流。","id":391,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"......","id":393,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":394},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":395},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":396},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bullet_loading","id":397},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"不确定是否具有感染性，无法确定行为模式是否会随时间变化，危险程度未知。","id":399,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"根据公证所相关条例，为保障公民权益，准许现场击杀难以判定级别的威胁。","id":400,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"......","id":402,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"没有反抗表现，疑似没有求生欲望。","id":404,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"失礼了，我会尽可能减轻痛感。","id":405,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":406},{"type":"charslot","id":407},{"type":"text","text":"怪物伫立在原地。","id":408},{"type":"text","text":"眼前是被阻塞的前路，身后是无法回头的曾经。","id":409},{"type":"text","text":"一切辩白与嘶吼、苦痛与不甘都在穿透坚硬表皮展露在外之前，被消化在这具已脱离人类范畴的躯体之内。","id":410},{"type":"text","text":"异化的怪物在无法逾越的阻力面前，失去所有力气，却又坚持不肯放下最后一点尊严。","id":411},{"type":"text","text":"它只是沉默着，静立着。","id":412},{"type":"text","text":"宛如一尊雕像。","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"等等！","id":414,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"dialog","id":415},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"all","id":416},{"type":"delay","time":"0.2","id":417},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"1","id":418},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","duration":"0.5","id":419},{"type":"delay","time":"0.8","id":420},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"别动手！执行者阁下！","id":422,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":423},{"type":"charslot","id":424},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":425},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"......","id":426,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“扭曲的怪物”","text":"......杰拉......尔德......","id":427,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":428},{"type":"charslot","id":429},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":430},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":431},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"......赫曼。你知道吗，我差点都想学着斯特凡诺他们祈祷了——祈祷执行者阁下说的“怪物”不会是你。","id":432,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":433},{"type":"charslot","id":434},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":435},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫曼","text":"......","id":436,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":437},{"type":"charslot","id":438},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":439},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"这是最合乎逻辑的推论。现在也已经得到证实。","id":441,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"让开，杰拉尔德。","id":442,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我不能让。","id":444,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":445},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......恕我直言，这是妨碍公务。","id":446,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":447},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我很清楚。你随时可以朝我扣下扳机，除掉我这个有罪的萨卡兹，我绝不会有怨言。","id":448,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"但我不能让你对赫曼动手。","id":449,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......理由。","id":451,"figure":["avg_1032_excu2_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我给不了你一个“正当”或是“合理”的理由。","id":453,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"我能说的只有——","id":454,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"看看赫曼身后。在那层门板后面，现在正睡着两个孩子。","id":455,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":456},{"type":"charslot","id":457},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_930_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫曼","text":"啊......孩子......","id":459,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫曼","text":"我的、孩子......","id":460,"figure":["avg_npc_930_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":461},{"type":"charslot","id":462},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":463},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"......","id":465,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"他们对发生了什么一无所知，期待你能够找到他们的母亲。","id":467,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"他们信任你。","id":468,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":469},{"type":"charslot","id":470},{"type":"text","text":"一个萨卡兹，用他饱经风霜的、粗糙的手，按住了一个萨科塔握着铳的手。","id":471},{"type":"text","text":"不带兄弟间的亲近与依赖，没有伙伴间的信任与理解。","id":472},{"type":"text","text":"但萨卡兹确实按住了萨科塔的手。","id":473},{"type":"text","text":"铳口一寸寸垂下。","id":474},{"type":"dialog","id":475},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1032_excu2_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":476},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_926_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":477},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"别动手。执行者阁下。","id":478,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"杰拉尔德","text":"在你能得出结论，说服你自己之前，别动手。","id":479,"figure":["avg_npc_926_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":480},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":481},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":482},{"type":"charslot","id":483},{"type":"image","id":484}],"characters":["修道院主教","？？？","杰拉尔德","费德里科","扭曲的怪物","艾伦戴尔","艾丝塔拉","“扭曲的怪物”","里凯莱","克莱芒","莱蒙德","赫曼"]}